short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Export Found Lab Caches as GPX file for import into GSAK.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds functionality to the Geocaching Adventure Lab Finds web page to export all Lab Cache finds as a GPX file. This file can then be imported into GSAK. A companion GSAK macro is then used to fill in other info that is not available on the web page.
